Privacy Policy
for the Canada Citizenship Tests
developed by Berdnikov Artem

This application has the advertisements, hence it collects and safely transmits the user's advertisement identifier to the Google AdMob.
The reason for that is to provide users with more relevant advertisements. This application does`t store user advertisement identifiers on its own.
This application doesn`t use and/or collect and/or store and/or transmit any other confidential or personal information.

ATTENTION!
The applicaion or/and the developer don't represent any government entity.
Source of government information is https://www.canada.ca/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/become-canadian-citizen/citizenship-test.html
This application is NOT an official government test. It is the sets of MOCK tests based on the official preparation guidence.
